FEATURES
========

 * 2 pass assembler
 * Inspired by AVR syntax / instruction set
 * Recursive macro lookups
 * Recursive file imports
 * Recursive numerical operations

WEAKNESSES
==========

 * Entirely case insensitive
 * No address management of DSEG
 * Single global namespace for all lookups
 * Line orientated
 * Uninformative error messages

DATA SEGMENT
============

Syntax:

  <label>: <type> <size>

Where <type>:

      .BYTE
      .WORD

Examples:

  foobar: .BYTE 3

 * Data is aligned to word size

LOGICAL OPERATIONS
==================

A + B           Addition
A - B           Subtraction
A & B           Bitwise AND
A | B           Bitwise OR
A ^ B           Bitwise XOR
-A              Negative A
~A              One's complement
